name: Catapult for Hire
blurb: Feel like a kid again in this Nintendo 64 era world.

rewards.reward: FOLLOW - Thanks for dropping by! Let's stay in touch ok? You can follow the project and get updates.
EARLY BIRD - Get a DRM-free game download (+Steam if greenlit) for an insane 50% off Kickstarter-only discount!
GAME ONLY - Get a DRM-free game download (+Steam if greenlit) for a special 33% off Kickstarter-only discount!
GAME PLUS - 1) Get the game. 2) Your name in a special thanks section on the Catapult for Hire website.
AUDIOPHILE - 1) Get the game + soundtrack. 2) Your name in a special thanks section on the Catapult for Hire website.
WALL OF AWESOME - 1) Get the game + soundtrack. 2) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

EARLY ACCESS + PUBLIC BETA - 1) Get the game + soundtrack. 2) Get early access to the game and give feedback that will help shape the finished product. 3) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

VISIONARY (HD making-of videos) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access. 2) Get HD timelapse videos showing how the game was made. 3) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

FABLED (Design an artifact) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access + HD timelapse videos. 2) Design a custom artifact to be hidden in the game world. These artifacts are used in crafting recipes for higher level catapults and payloads. 3) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

ANCIENT (Design a rare artifact) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access + HD timelapse videos. 2) Design a custom epic-level artifact to be hidden in the game world. These artifacts are harder to find and give bonuses like extra catapult power, faster rotation speed and larger bomb radius. 3) Get behind the scenes access to the game\u2019s assets, art, reference and code samples at your request! Ask about anything and see how the game was made. 4) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

CHIMERICAL (Design a creature) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access + HD timelapse videos + behind the scenes access 2) Design a creature to be used in the game! 3)  Draw a picture or just describe an idea and I\u2019ll make it a fully animated, interactive ready-to-hit 3D creature with a belly full of gold in the game! 4) Get behind the scenes access to the game\u2019s assets, art, reference and code samples at your request! Ask about anything and see how the game was made. 5) Get a copy of the finished model in your preferred file format. 6) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

MYTHOLOGICAL (Design a client character) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access + HD timelapse videos + behind the scenes access. 2) Design a client with dialogue to be used in the game! 3) Design (at least) 2 missions based on your client. 4) Get a copy of the finished model in your preferred file format. 5) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.

EPIC (Design a Catapult) - 1) Get the game + soundtrack + early access + HD timelapse videos + behind the scenes access. 2) Design a rare catapult to be used in the game! You come up with its identity, mythology, strengths / weaknesses and together we'll plan how it is located / unlocked in the game. 3) Get a copy of the finished model in your preferred file format. 4) Your name in a special thanks section of the game and website.
